Package org.cyclops.integratedterminals.api.ingredient

Interface IIngredientInstanceSorter<T>

All Superinterfaces:
Comparator<T>
All Known Implementing Classes:
FluidStackIdSorter, FluidStackNameSorter, FluidStackQuantitySorter, IngredientInstanceSorterAdapter, ItemStackIdSorter, ItemStackNameSorter, ItemStackQuantitySorter
public interface IIngredientInstanceSorter<T> extends Comparator<T>
A sorting comparator for ingredient instances. These don't have to be 0-equals-safe, meaning that non-equal instances don't necessarily have to return a non-0 value. This is because these sorters are typically chained.
